title: Episode 92: The Mysterious Death of Jessica Renee Johnson Mini Morbid
description:
This one is a real head scratcher. Jessica Johnson, a 37 year old single mother,  is found hanging from a mailbox in broad daylight. Police immediately label it a bizarre suicide but almost all of the evidence points to something much more sinister.

The Facebook page Jessica's mother Linda set up:
https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Interest/What-happened-to-Jessica-Johnson-886316114880842/
